{"tid":1375590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：黎明之前嘅黑暗，係至撚黑暗。但係黎明即將會來臨。","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T06:05:09.000Z","uid":36592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c905378b92f4006c950f813525cc6bb61cb42e2c","tid":1375590,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA?t=1235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA%3Ft%3D1235&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=36ce5bee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA?t=1235</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QaYjS0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQaYjS0K.png&h=5a0e18f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>堅持五大訴求</ins></strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"964a7fa991564327de4d0fa89630a46a2acf3a28","tid":1375590,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"香港人冇忘記天琦，革命嘅種子正在萌芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542320522ac4b8e04dd92e227bb043ddaab14ba0","tid":1375590,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd256ba9e178b92df6d3d752e65f61f82d418bd3","tid":1375590,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542320522ac4b8e04dd92e227bb043ddaab14ba0","tid":1375590,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"re